metadata.name: Mr. Smith's House
metadata.description: Mr. and Mrs. Smith are a couple of detectives who deal with dark affairs. Their home is a modern building with neon lighting and their most remarkable feature is their car, called Black Lightning. It is a high-performance vehicle specially designed to ensure the couple's safety, with armored glass, explosion-resistant tires, and weapon systems. Black Lightning reflects their brave and resolute nature and plays a crucial role in their success in tackling dangerous missions.
